  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "He will get more than 140 votes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Minister Vajira Abeywardhana has said that the acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe will get more than 140 votes in the presidential election to be held in Parliament.",
        "He said that he is leading discussions with other parties including the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna as the United National Party's secretary.",
        "He said that he will get more votes and be elected as the President and take office with the blessings of all.",
        "If Ranil Wickremesinghe is elected as the 9th Executive President of Sri Lanka, he will make Sri Lanka the best country in Asia. He will make it the best country in the world.",
        "He said that because the leader has 50 years of experience in politics, there should be no mistrust and panic on him."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
